/>\n我想知d阿伯有冇西玩</blockquote><br />\n連部份都硬要打英文<br />\nAbc 岩岩番香港？</blockquote><br />\nP1p2你識條鐵咩，行撚埋一邊啦</blockquote><br />\nFor your reference<br />\nP你老母西<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/161339_144b3f7d248f94d8e2e3ee1fa384b0d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F161339_144b3f7d248f94d8e2e3ee1fa384b0d7.jpg&h=f19bb949&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有我真係未撚見過part既short form 係p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你柒夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為自己好撚醒<br />\n<br />\nFor your reference<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n費時你條傻尻唔明<br />\n我就畫公仔畫出腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家唔係唔比你用英文<br />\n而係笑尻你普遍香港人都唔會用英文黎代替既字眼- 例如梳<br />\n你就不停comb comb comb<br />\n<br />\n點解要笑柒你？<br />\n因為咁樣係本末倒置<br />\n一般人借助外語去論述係因為<br />\n母語冇相對既詞語（常見 潮流/意識）<br />\n泛用性問題（常發生在學術界）<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭就以為自己好撚醒咁<br />\n快d縮返入你母親的陰部 好嗎？"},{"pid":"f52cf5b258fd077b0645216e5cb8be0ec65227a8","tid":346484,"uid":117237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"屌拿星 <br />\n比條傻尻入黎倒亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f756fbf500b973ace2992c948f5169261c9959dd","tid":346484,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"即係你只要影響到香港人口語都跟你一齊<br />\nComb comb comb 我咪收皮囉"},{"pid":"530b251a9c466da7ce