ts/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為自己好撚醒<br />\n<br />\nFor your reference<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n費時你條傻尻唔明<br />\n我就畫公仔畫出腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家唔係唔比你用英文<br />\n而係笑尻你普遍香港人都唔會用英文黎代替既字眼- 例如梳<br />\n你就不停comb comb comb<br />\n<br />\n點解要笑柒你？<br />\n因為咁樣係本末倒置<br />\n一般人借助外語去論述係因為<br />\n母語冇相對既詞語（常見 潮流/意識）<br />\n泛用性問題（常發生在學術界）<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭就以為自己好撚醒咁<br />\n快d縮返入你母親的陰部 好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦柒頭<br />\nNotebook多人講定手提電腦/筆記簿呀<br />\nPc定桌上型電腦？<br />\n講英文方便 講英文就本末例置？<br />\n你條柒頭就真係以為自己好撚醒 搬龍門咁撚叻"},{"pid":"d9abc8e74428a24cb708cd121398809acc29d8bd","tid":346484,"uid":9387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌拿星 <br />\n比條傻尻入黎倒亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搗呀 中文達人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7cee3ae68bbcef827b1c7d3ff36997bdf04445","tid":346484,"uid":9387,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"ssp做咩唔打中文深水埗呀<br />\n學術性定係母語無相應既詞語？<br />\n自打嘴巴毫無邏輯可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12e9e1ffbbb1b347a6d8f31a06d585984f18597","tid":346484,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次食愛文生見到d大媽係咁姣d廢老，食慾即刻減半</blockquote><br />\n其實油麻地都好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f95149d66ac7e2a6942b98e2591787f27858d38","tid":346484,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":